2000-07-28  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Added the 'make package-source' target, for building
	a source package.

2000-07-22  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Added support for adding auxiliary C compiler flags.

2000-07-20  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Finished the kernel support. Now, building storm with
	autochaos works just fine!

2000-07-09  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Started working on multi-directory support. Still
	lots of work to be done, though..

2000-07-08  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos.sgml: Started writing some documentation.

2000-07-03  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Added a function that makes config.h include all the
	library header files that are required by the package.

2000-06-17  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Added support for an <include> directive, for
	specifying additional paths to be searched for include files.
	Added support for automatic dependency management.

2000-06-15  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Added support for libraries (generating static
	archives, installing them and installing header files).  Added
	support for checking if autochaos is installed or not (to prepare
	for automatic regeneration of the configure script and
	everything).

2000-06-10  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* autochaos: Changed $input_file to "autochaos.rules", on request
	by Henrik Hallin.

2000-06-09  Per Lundberg  <plundis@chaosdev.org>

	* Started doing some serious work. The XML parsing part is almost
	complete. We now support checking the CPU type, and detecting
	available libraries, and some more.

